Program: Great Lives
Title: Thora Hird
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b008fwlc
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 28 Oct 2016
Series of biographical discussions with Matthew Parris. 1/7. Jan Ravens champions Dame Thora Hird. Biographer Morris Bright and Thora's daughter Janette Scott provide expert advice on an actress once described as the Queen Mum of British stage and screen.